---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import ChallengeFilter from '../components/ChallengeFilter'
---

<Layout title="品味挑战 — VibeCoder Learn">
  <section class="py-4 sm:py-8">
    <p class="font-mono text-sm text-rust mb-2 tracking-wide">TASTE CHALLENGES</p>
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">153 个品味挑战</h1>
    <p class="text-charcoal-light mb-1">品味不是天赋，是训练出来的。</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-warm-gray mb-8">12个维度 · 每个挑战 30-90 分钟 · 可反复做 · 点击卡片查看详情</p>

    <ChallengeFilter client:load locale="zh" />
  </section>
</Layout>
